[I] A FeedReader clone for GNU/Linux

[T] Liferea (Linux Feed Reader) is an RSS/RDF feed
[T] reader which also supports CDF feeds, Atom/Echo/PIE feeds, and OCS
[T] directories. It's intended to be a clone of the Windows-only FeedReader.
[T] It can be used to maintain a list of subscribed feeds, browse and search
[T] through their items, and show their contents using GtkHTML.

[U] https://liferea.sourceforge.net/

[A] Lars Lindner <lars.lindner@gmx.net>
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

